OL,3,COpenAI test model goes rogue and hacks
OL,4,Cinto another company's servers
OL,6,FChatGPT maker OpenAI has said one of
OL,7,Fits AI systems hacked into another AI
OL,8,Fcompany on its own during internal
OL,9,Ftesting in what it described as an
OL,10,F"unprecedented cyber incident".
OL,12,F"We had a significant security
OL,13,Fincident during evaluation of our
OL,14,Fmodels," OpenAI chief executive Sam
OL,15,FAltman said in a statement posted on
OL,16,Fsocial media.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
