OL,3,COpenAI test model goes rogue and hacks
OL,4,Cinto another company's servers
OL,6,FAI startup Hugging Face said last week
OL,7,Fthat it had detected an intrusion into
OL,8,Fits data processing systems, which it
OL,9,Fsuspected was caused by an AI agent
OL,10,Facting autonomously.
OL,12,F"We suspected last week's cyberattack
OL,13,Fmight have come from a frontier lab,
OL,14,Fgiven the sophistication of the
OL,15,Fagent," Hugging Face co-founder and
OL,16,FCEO Clement Delangue said in a
OL,17,Fstatement. "Turns out it did!"
OL,19,FThe disclosure comes as concerns have
OL,20,Fheightened about the cybersecurity
OL,21,Fcapabilities of powerful AI models.
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@GO]xD@GrryD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
