PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784791090
OL,3,COpenAI test model goes rogue and hacks
OL,4,Cinto another company's servers
OL,6,FThis led US President Donald Trump in
OL,7,FJune to sign an executive order
OL,8,Fcreating a framework for the federal
OL,9,Fgovernment to assess the national
OL,10,Fsecurity risks of the most advanced AI
OL,11,Fsystems for up to a month before their
OL,12,Fpublic release.
OL,14,F"AI is accelerating the discovery and
OL,15,Fexploitation of vulnerabilities,"
OL,16,FOpenAI said in its statement Tuesday.
OL,18,F"The primary lesson from this incident
OL,19,Fis that model security and safety must
OL,20,Fkeep pace with rapidly advancing
OL,21,Fcapabilities."
OL,26,@vD@AOUwD@aO]zD@AOU}D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
