OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784791090
OL,3,COpenAI test model goes rogue and hacks
OL,4,Cinto another company's servers
OL,6,FDelangue, who said he spent the past
OL,7,F24 hours working with OpenAI, added:
OL,8,F"We strongly believe there was no
OL,9,Fmalicious intent on their part. It's
OL,10,Fquite mind-blowing that all of this
OL,11,Fhappened autonomously!"
OL,13,FHe added that it "might be the first
OL,14,Fincident of its kind."
OL,16,FOpenAI said the intrusion was caused
OL,17,Fby a combination of its AI models,
OL,18,Fincluding its newly released GPT5.6
OL,19,FSol and an "even more capable" model
OL,20,Fthat is still being tested internally.
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@ROUvD@VO]{D@LOU{D@^O]
