PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784791090
OL,3,COpenAI test model goes rogue and hacks
OL,4,Cinto another company's servers
OL,6,FIt added that its AI used stolen
OL,7,Fcredentials and discovered a
OL,8,Fpreviously unknown vulnerability to
OL,9,Faccess Hugging Face servers.
OL,11,FThe company said it went to "extreme
OL,12,Flengths to achieve a rather narrow
OL,13,Ftesting goal" and "found ways to gain
OL,14,Faccess to secret information that it
OL,15,Fcould use to cheat the evaluation".
